BuiltIn!

Shine:
${shine:[fade-in,stay,fade-out][primary-color,secondary-color]My text} (colour codes are placed in the primary and secondary section)
Marquee/Moving:
${marquee:[fade-in,stay,fade-out][marquee-width]My text}
Text Write Script:
${text_write:[fade-in,stay,fade-out]My text}
Text delete Script:
${text_delete:[fade-in,stay,fade-out]My text}
Countdown Script:
${count_down:[fade-in,stay,fade-out]10}  (10 is the srating number, CAN BE CHANGED)
Countup Script:
${count_up:[fade-in,stay,fade-out]10} (10 is the srating number, CAN BE CHANGED)
